snippet: An explosion at a condo complex in central New Jersey killed a woman and damaged dozens of homes, officials said.
abstract: Gas explosion at condominium complex in Ewing Township, New Jersey, kills one woman and damages dozens of homes; utility company PSE&G says cause of explosion is under investigation.
lead_paragraph: An explosion at a condo complex in central New Jersey killed a woman and damaged dozens of homes, officials said.

headline.main: One Killed in Gas Explosion at Condo Complex
headline.print_headline: One Killed in Blast at Condo Complex
